		<!-- 宜居区域文本 -->
		
		<Replace Tag="LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_JNR_UC_DISTRICT_HAPPINESS_CHAPTER_JNRDHABASE_TITLE" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>宜居区域（魅力值模组）</Text>
		</Replace>
		
		<Replace Tag="LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_JNR_UC_DISTRICT_HAPPINESS_CHAPTER_JNRDHABASE_PARA_1" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>“宜居区域”可根据区域单元格的魅力值为城市提供宜居度。一名健康的劳动者一定过得很愉快，如果能让他们在美丽干净的环境中生活和工作，您的公民会很感激。魅力值来源已重新设计。</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Tag="LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_JNR_UC_DISTRICT_HAPPINESS_CHAPTER_JNRDHABASE_PARA_2" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>一个区域根据其单元格的魅力值提供 [ICON_Amenities] 宜居度：[NEWLINE][NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]惊艳的（4）：+1 [ICON_Amenities] 宜居度。[NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]无吸引力的（-2）：-1 [ICON_Amenities] 宜居度。[NEWLINE ][ICON_Bullet]令人厌恶的（-4）：-2 [ICON_Amenities] 宜居度。[NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]泛滥平原单元格的魅力值比实际低1点（即阈值分别为5、-1、-3）。</Text>
		</Replace>
		
		<Replace Tag="LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_JNR_UC_DISTRICT_HAPPINESS_CHAPTER_JNRDHASOURCES_TITLE" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>魅力值来源的变化</Text>
		</Replace>
		
		<Replace Tag="LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_JNR_UC_DISTRICT_HAPPINESS_CHAPTER_JNRDHASOURCES_PARA_1" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>对魅力值来源进行了以下更改：[NEWLINE][NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]泛滥平原（草原、平原、沙漠）：不再对相邻单元格提供-1魅力值。[NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]礁石：为相邻单元格提供+1魅力值。[NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]地热裂缝：为相邻单元格提供+1魅力值。[NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]火山：有火山的山脉不再为相邻单元格提供+1魅力值。</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Tag="LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_JNR_UC_DISTRICT_HAPPINESS_CHAPTER_JNRDHASOURCES_PARA_2" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>完成市政“保护地球”后出现以下变化：[NEWLINE][NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]沼泽：为相邻单元格提供+1魅力值而非-1魅力值。[NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]森林：若未被改良（！），则额外对相邻单元格提供+1魅力值。</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Tag="LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_JNR_UC_DISTRICT_HAPPINESS_CHAPTER_JNRDHASOURCES_PARA_3" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>对改良设施进行了以下更改：[NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]地热发电厂：修建有地热发电厂的地热裂缝不再为相邻单元格提供+1魅力值。</Text>
		</Replace>
		
		<Replace Tag="LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_JNR_UC_DISTRICT_HAPPINESS_CHAPTER_JNRDHABALANCE_TITLE" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>平衡性调整</Text>
		</Replace>
		
		<Replace Tag="LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_JNR_UC_DISTRICT_HAPPINESS_CHAPTER_JNRDHABALANCE_PARA_1" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>为了维持游戏平衡，进行了以下更改：[NEWLINE][ICON_Bullet]埃菲尔铁塔：帝国境内所有单元格+1魅力值。</Text>
		</Replace>
		
